## Summary Card Variables

These variables populate the **cover page** (Report No., Assessment Date, Location, SIC, NAICS) and the **executive summary**. The values are typically found in the **assessment request form** for the facility, located in the Teams folder.

```latex
\newcommand{\PlantLocation}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantSIC}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantNAICS}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantSquareFeet}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantPersonnel}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantOperationDays}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantOperationWeeks}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantOperationHours}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantEnergySources}{--}
\newcommand{\PlantAnnualSales}{--}
```

| Variable | What to enter |
|---|---|
| `\PlantLocation` | City and state of the facility (no street address) |
| `\PlantSIC` | Standard Industrial Classification code |
| `\PlantNAICS` | North American Industry Classification System code |
| `\PlantSquareFeet` | Total facility floor area in square feet |
| `\PlantPersonnel` | Number of employees at the facility |
| `\PlantOperationDays` | Operating days per week |
| `\PlantOperationWeeks` | Operating weeks per year |
| `\PlantOperationHours` | Operating hours per day |
| `\PlantEnergySources` | Energy sources used at the facility (e.g., *Electricity, Natural Gas*) |
| `\PlantAnnualSales` | Annual sales figure for the facility |

